extends layout

block content
  .help-page
    .help-top
      .help-banner
        h1 Need Help?
        p Find answers, learn how to use the website, and get support for your account and gaming posts.
      .help-image
        img(src="/images/help-side.jpg", alt="help")

    .help-grid
      .help-card
        h3 Account Help
        p Learn how to create an account, log in, and manage your profile settings safely.
      .help-card
        h3 Posting Tips
        p Need help posting or editing a tip? This section guides you through creating quality content.
      .help-card
        h3 Saved Tips
        p You can bookmark useful tips and revisit them later from your saved tips page.
      .help-card
        h3 Contact Support
        p For technical issues, broken pages, or other concerns, use the Tell Us form on the About page.

    .faq-box
      h2 Frequently Asked Questions

      .faq-item
        h4 How do I save a tip?
        p Open the three-dot menu on a tip and choose Save Tip.

      .faq-item
        h4 Can I edit any tip?
        p No. You can only edit or delete your own tips.

      .faq-item
        h4 Why can I not comment?
        p You must be logged in before posting comments.

      .faq-item
        h4 Where can I find my saved tips?
        p Open the Saved / Bookmarked Tips page from the homepage sidebar.